---
title: BBQ Pulled Chicken with cheesy wedges and tomato salsa
description: The process of 'pulling' chicken, beef, or pork is popular in BBQ style cooking.  It's a way of tenderising the meat, giving it a new texture and unlocking more flavour. In this recipe, even more taste and texture are added by the tangy tomato salsa that tops this cheesy BBQ dish.
